Package com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management

The com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management package provides interfaces for managing Namespaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClusterAvailableVersions
    The ClusterAvailableVersions interface provides methods to retrieve available upgrade versions of WCP and detailed information about each upgrade.
    ClusterAvailableVersionsTypes
    The ClusterAvailableVersions interface provides methods to retrieve available upgrade versions of WCP and detailed information about each upgrade.

    The ClusterCompatibility interface provides methods to get Namespace-related compatibility information for clusters in this vCenter.
    Clusters
    The Clusters interface provides methods to enable and disable vSphere Namespaces on a vSphere cluster.

    The ClusterSizeInfo interface provides methods to retrieve various sizes available for enabling Namespaces and information about each size.
